data.description: This updated home sits on a large lot at the end of town.  Plenty of room for outdoor activities.  Many updates to the home, and the kitchen/dining area is the bomb!  Open concept with custom cabinetry and solid 6 panel doors.  Main floor master bedroom and laundry.  Walkout lower level can be finished asyou want.
